(1280,	254,	'intro_paragraph',	'At our firm, we provide clear, commercially grounded legal advice to help businesses navigate local and regional laws with confidence. Whether you are launching a venture, entering into a contract or restructuring operations, our team offers legal clarity and strategic insight at every stage of your journey.\r\nWe support clients across a range of industries with <b>core legal services</b>, delivered with the responsiveness and care of a boutique firm and the technical depth of experienced legal practitioners.'),
