(1284,	254,	'contract_law_&_agreements',	'<strong>Contract Law &amp; Commercial Agreements</strong>\r\nWe draft, review and negotiate a wide variety of commercial agreements with a focus on clarity, enforceability and alignment with your business objectives:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Sale of goods and services contracts</li>\r\n 	<li>Shareholder and partnership agreements</li>\r\n 	<li>Joint ventures, NDAs and MOUs</li>\r\n 	<li>Agency and distribution agreements</li>\r\n 	<li>Employment and consultancy agreements</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nOur goal is to ensure your contracts are not only legally sound but also commercially viable and practically enforceable.'),
(1285,	254,	'_contract_law_&_agreements',	'field_686a1102ffd0e'),
(1286,	254,	'corporate_&_regulatory_advisory',	'<strong>Corporate &amp; Regulatory Advisory</strong>\r\nWe support companies with ongoing legal advisory services related to:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Corporate governance and compliance</li>\r\n 	<li>UAE Federal and Emirate-level laws</li>\r\n 	<li>Free zone and offshore company laws</li>\r\n 	<li>Foreign investment restrictions and structuring</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nWhere relevant, we work alongside your business or finance teams to ensure alignment between legal requirements and operational realities.'),
(1287,	254,	'_corporate_&_regulatory_advisory',	'field_686a1110ffd0f'),
(1288,	254,	'tailored_legal_solutions',	'Our firm combines sector-specific understanding with local legal expertise to offer tailored advice. Whether you need a quick review or long-term counsel, we ensure your legal needs are met with efficiency and insight.'),
(1289,	254,	'_tailored_legal_solutions',	'field_686a111dffd10'),
(1290,	254,	'integrated_legal_support',	'We also offer legal services that complement our wider offerings, including:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>IP Protection</li>\r\n 	<li>Corporate Structuring &amp; Business Setup</li>\r\n 	<li>Compliance Training and Regulatory Workshops</li>\r\n 	<li>Labour and Employment Advisory</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nThese services are designed to provide clients with end-to-end legal support across the life cycle of a business.\r\n\r\nOur integrated approach ensures that businesses receive consistent, strategic legal guidance at every stage of their growth.'),
