(2279,	55,	'_included_title',	'field_686bfd1022d00'),
(2280,	55,	'included_description',	'<ul>\r\n  <li><strong>Personalised Call Answering:</strong> Provide your own welcome message and we will ensure every client is greeted in a warm and consistent manner that reflects your brand identity.</li>\r\n  <li><strong>Dedicated Local Phone Number (04):</strong> Build trust and credibility with a dedicated Dubai landline. Your clients will always have a professional number to call - no more personal mobile numbers or missed business opportunities.</li>\r\n  <li><strong>24/7 Availability:</strong> Our multilingual receptionist team is available around the clock to handle calls from both local and international clients, ensuring your business stays connected across time zones.</li>\r\n  <li><strong>Intelligent Call Handling:</strong> We route calls to the appropriate departments, take detailed messages and provide responses to general inquiries - just like an in-house receptionist, but without the overhead.</li>\r\n</ul>'),
(2281,	55,	'_included_description',	'field_686bff1522d01'),
(2282,	55,	'why_choose_title',	'Why Choose a Virtual Receptionist?'),
(2283,	55,	'_why_choose_title',	'field_686bff2e22d02'),
(2284,	55,	'why_choose_description',	'As the business world increasingly embraces remote operations, outsourcing non-core functions like reception has become a smart, cost-effective solution. Here is why entrepreneurs and SMEs in the UAE are turning to virtual receptionists:\r\n<ul>\r\n  <li><strong>Reduce Startup Costs:</strong> Hiring in-house staff can be expensive. Outsourcing receptionist services allows you to save on salaries, office space and training, without compromising on professionalism.</li>\r\n  <li><strong>Project a Stronger Brand Image:</strong> Using a landline and having a professional receptionist answer every call makes your business look more established and trustworthy.</li>\r\n  <li><strong>Improve Productivity:</strong> Let our team handle your calls while you focus on growing your business. Fewer interruptions mean more time for strategy, sales and operations.</li>\r\n  <li><strong>Ensure 24/7 Responsiveness:</strong> Whether your clients are in the UAE, Asia, Europe or North America - our receptionists are available 24/7 so your business never sleeps.</li>\r\n  <li><strong>Enhance Customer Experience:</strong> Real people answering the phone builds trust and loyalty. Clients appreciate speaking to a human who can provide answers or escalate issues as needed.</li>\r\n  <li><strong>Never Miss Important Calls:</strong> Every message is logged and delivered to you promptly, helping ensure follow-ups happen and opportunities aren’t lost.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n'),
(2285,	55,	'_why_choose_description',	'field_686bff4622d03'),
(2286,	55,	'it_time_title',	'Is It Time for a Virtual Receptionist?'),
(2287,	55,	'_it_time_title',	'field_686bff6122d04'),
(2288,	55,	'it_time_description',	'You may need a virtual receptionist if:\r\n<ul>\r\n  <li>You are still using your personal number for business calls</li>\r\n  <li>You are overwhelmed with inquiries and missing calls</li>\r\n  <li>You don’t have time or budget to hire a full-time employee</li>\r\n  <li>Your productivity is impacted by frequent phone interruptions</li>\r\n  <li>You need a professional local presence in Dubai</li>\r\n  <li>You operate across time zones and want 24/7 call handling</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n'),
(2289,	55,	'_it_time_description',	'field_686bff6822d05'),
(2290,	55,	'help',	'We don’t just offer virtual receptionist services, we offer peace of mind. Whether you are launching a new business or expanding your operations in the UAE, our support services are designed to simplify your journey. Contact us today to find out more.'),
